JSON string.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Resolved vertx-web-client 5.0.1 uses Vert.x core 5.0.1 with Netty 4.2.2.Final; normal WebClient coverage can use an in-process Vert.x HTTP server, but Java 25 native runs need Netty unsafe-access system properties.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Set native test runtime system properties for 5.0.1 as for the existing 5.0.0 scaffold: -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true. Prefer local Vert.x HttpServer endpoints for GET/POST, JSON codecs, forms/multipart, redirects, sessions, caching, and streaming; no Docker service is needed. Avoid OAuth2WebClient unless deliberately adding its optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2 dependency.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The failing issue is specifically a native-image run on JDK 25/current-defaults, so JVM tests alone may pass without exposing the missing Netty runtime properties.\",\n    \"Keep the unsafe-access properties scoped to Vert.x 5.0.x or the Netty 4.2.x path; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b368e0efbdd98a8016a40613e7f5481949924960f7a8f8589\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3475, "output": 768, "cacheRead": 22528, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26771, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782604084982, "responseId": "resp_0b368e0efbdd98a8016a40613597508194ab73020e0c3f88c4"}, "toolResults": []}
